Chile Plans to Fast-Track Bill on Derivatives, Correa Says

-- B y   R a n d y   W o o d s
-- 
2011-02-28T19:36:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/chile-plans-to-fast-track-bill-on-derivatives-correa-says.html
Chile plans to fast-track a bill on
derivatives as it seeks ways to make the instruments more
accessible to small companies, Pablo Correa, capital markets
coordinator at the  Finance Ministry , told reporters today in
Santiago.  To contact the reporter responsible on this story:
Randy Woods in Santiago at 
 rwoods13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
